      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior paint has several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but the upholstery shows significant wear, including some minor staining on the rear seats and worn floor mats. Mechanically, the car is operational and starts reliably, though the engine would benefit from a tune-up and the tires will likely need replacement within the next few months. It serves as a practical, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a daily commuter who is comfortable with cosmetic imperfections and upcoming maintenance needs.",
