      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This specimen boasts comprehensive mechanical provenance, including a reinforced rear subframe, proactive rod bearing replacement, and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. The chassis maintains factory-spec rigidity with zero bushing deflection, while the speed-sensitive limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Meticulously maintained with a flawless service history, this is a turn-key example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated engineering",
